15/07/2020.short_text: Stop all conversation with the BJP and head back to your home in Jaipur, the Congress impressed upon Sachin Pilot in yet another outreach attempt. The state has been teetering on the edge since Pilot made his differences with chief minister Ashok Gehlot public.
